<paragraph blockId="3.[151,629,413,439]" box="[151,629,413,439]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,629,413,439]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,629,413,439]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Balogh, 1962" authorityName="Balogh" authorityYear="1962" box="[286,629,413,439]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Hymenobelba Balogh, 1962</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="65" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,485,922]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">
The genus (
<taxonomicName authority="Balogh, 1962" authorityName="Balogh" authorityYear="1962" box="[293,627,485,511]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[293,458,485,510]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Hymenobelba</emphasis>
Balogh, 1962
</taxonomicName>
was established based on specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[1144,1290,485,511]" name="Madagascar" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
. Among the species assigned to this genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Balogh et Mahunka, 1966" authorityName="Balogh et Mahunka" authorityYear="1966" box="[509,954,522,548]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulus">
<emphasis box="[509,638,522,547]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. annulus</emphasis>
Balogh et Mahunka, 1966
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Balogh et Mahunka, 1966" authorityName="Balogh et Mahunka" authorityYear="1966" box="[967,1431,522,548]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coarctata">
<emphasis box="[967,1115,522,547]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. coarctata</emphasis>
Balogh et Mahunka, 1966
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Covarrubias, 1967" authorityName="Covarrubias" authorityYear="1967" box="[151,545,560,586]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flagellata">
<emphasis box="[151,307,560,585]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. flagellata</emphasis>
Covarrubias, 1967
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Covarrubias, 1967" authorityName="Covarrubias" authorityYear="1967" box="[560,951,560,586]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ramulosa">
<emphasis box="[560,713,560,585]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. ramulosa</emphasis>
Covarrubias, 1967
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Luxton, 1988" authorityName="Luxton" authorityYear="1988" box="[966,1340,560,586]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="diversisetosa">
<emphasis box="[966,1164,560,585]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. diversisetosa</emphasis>
Luxton, 1988
</taxonomicName>
) do not belong in this genus because J. Balogh &amp; P. Balogh (1992) relegated 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Covarrubias" authorityYear="1967" box="[966,1114,597,622]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flagellata">
<emphasis box="[966,1114,597,622]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. flagellata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the newly erected genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. &amp; P. Balogh" authorityYear="1992" box="[151,294,634,659]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Ctenamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,294,634,659]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Ctenamerus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J. et P. Balogh, 1992, and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Balogh et Mahunka" authorityYear="1966" box="[614,745,634,659]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulus">
<emphasis box="[614,745,634,659]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">H. annulus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as 
<typeStatus box="[786,837,634,660]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">type</typeStatus>
species for the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. &amp; P. Balogh" authorityYear="1992" box="[1103,1249,634,659]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Haplamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1103,1249,634,659]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Haplamerus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J. et P. Balogh, 1992. 
<bibRefCitation author="Subias, L. S." box="[226,393,672,698]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" pagination="3 - 305" refId="ref3477" refString="Subias, L. S. (2009) Listado sistematico, sinonimico y biogeografico de los acaros oribatidos (Acariformes, Oribatida) del Mundo (exepto fosiles). Originally published in Graellsia 60, 3 - 305, 2004, actualized april 2009), 547 pp. Available from http: // www. ucm. es / info / zoo / Artropodos / Catalogo. pdf (last access 1 May 2010)" type="book chapter" year="2009">Subías (2009)</bibRefCitation>
accepted the latter opinion, however he considered the other mentioned species as the original genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Balogh" authorityYear="1962" box="[325,488,709,734]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[325,488,709,734]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Hymenobelba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,485,922]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">
In my opinion— without a thorough study of the specimens—this point of view is acceptable. However, I propose classifying 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Balogh et Mahunka" authorityYear="1966" box="[394,684,784,809]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coarctata">
<emphasis box="[394,684,784,809]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Hymenobelba coarctata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. &amp; P. Balogh" authorityYear="1992" box="[849,997,784,809]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Haplamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[849,997,784,809]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Haplamerus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authority="(Balogh et Mahunka, 1966)" authorityName="Mahunka" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Balogh et Mahunka" baseAuthorityYear="1966" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Haplamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coarctatus" status="comb. n.">
<emphasis box="[1017,1300,784,809]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Haplamerus coarctatus</emphasis>
(Balogh et Mahunka, 1966)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[362,470,821,847]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" rank="species">comb. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
] and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Covarrubias" authorityYear="1967" box="[540,832,821,846]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ramulosa">
<emphasis box="[540,832,821,846]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Hymenobelba ramulosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. &amp; P. Balogh" authorityYear="1992" box="[999,1146,821,846]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Ctenamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[999,1146,821,846]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Ctenamerus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authority="(Covarrubias, 1967)" authorityName="Mahunka" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Covarrubias" baseAuthorityYear="1967" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Ctenamerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ramulosa" status="comb. n.">
<emphasis box="[1165,1435,821,846]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Ctenamerus ramulosa</emphasis>
(Covarrubias, 1967)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[424,541,858,884]" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" rank="species">comb. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
]. The position of 
<taxonomicName authority="Luxton, 1988" authorityName="Luxton" authorityYear="1988" box="[780,1324,858,884]" class="Arachnida" family="Ameridae" genus="Hymenobelba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="diversisetosa">
<emphasis box="[780,1138,858,883]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="65">Hymenobelba diversisetosa</emphasis>
Luxton, 1988
</taxonomicName>
remains questionable.
</paragraph>
